{"tid":1681622,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"好嬲!!!呢間店咁都仲有咁多人排？","createTime":"2019-10-29T14:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T16:51:10.000Z","uid":325022,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"51aa5ceb0ba9a84f5c2a2cc3b596f0b5275cfd1f","tid":1681622,"uid":325022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:13:57.000Z","msg":"話說小弟我同朋友食飯就去咗西九食晚飯<br />\n就去咗水門泰式海南雞飯食<br />\n哇 一去到就見到勁多人排隊<br />\n咁佢係黃店 咁我都唔介意排隊既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n排排下 冇啦啦勁多人離隊<br />\n我心諗咩事 就行到去隊頭啦<br />\n見到佢得返學生餐 咁我咪出示學生證囉<br />\n屌！講起就嬲 我嗌兩個學生餐<br />\n頂佢個肺 唔收我錢喎！<br />\n咁我咪嗌跟嘢飲 佢話本身個餐已經跟喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我就話加飯囉<br />\n(諗住要加錢咁就可以俾錢佢地啦)<br />\n點知又話唔洗錢喎<br />\n真係好嬲！下次唔出示學生證啦<br />\n懲罰下啲黃店 大家記得幫襯小店呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rSXnq7r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSXnq7r.png&h=1219d40d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5a05b266451fd231faff06d3c85e7c4a716aa90","tid":1681622,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:14:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5c1bed95ccac225b1273f1f7c583f55acf466329","tid":1681622,"uid":31094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:15:33.000Z","msg":"個老闆真係好撚柒寸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020b89bf75f1ebecd010f9c0e32ae6e962c0fab4","tid":1681622,"uid":325022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"